'''Galactic Gamers''' is a League of Legends team from Mexico.

== History ==
'''[[Galactic Gamers]]''' was formed in September 2015, when '''[[Gaming Gaming]]''' renamed. The first four players announced were {{bl|Oddie}}, {{bl|Don Cholo (Sergio Salas)|Don Cholo}}, {{bl|1an}}, and {{bl|Gyga}} four members of Gaming Gaming roster. 

